snippet.title: Dance with the Teletubbies (2003) DVD Games
snippet.description:
As promised in my previous video, I decided to post the "Dance with the Teletubbies" DVD games in higher quality and left out some unseen footage.
It's kinda petty how neither Tinky Winky nor Dipsy was seen in the counting game, only the female Teletubbies. Why didn't they add the males, too?
